# 10. Test Database Connection

Create a temporary file named `testConnection.js` in the `backend` folder:

```javascript
const db = require("./config/db");

db.query("SELECT * FROM climatic_zones", (err, result) => {
    if (err) {
        console.log(err);
    } else {
        console.log(result);
    }

    process.exit();
});
```

Run:

```bash
node testConnection.js
```


